        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/c/fbc32d/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2021-07-31T00:13:24.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"172420\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Terrific wine, this! But when you see the way the vineyards are farmed and the attention to detail in the winery, it isn\u2019t really a surprise. The wines age really well, too. I\u2019m publishing a vertical back to Bruno\u2019s first vintage, 48 different wines, today, as it happens!</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>And I just read it today, as it happens. Never heard of the estate before today. It doesn\u2019t appear to be easy to find in the US.</p>",
