        "created_at": "2022-11-11T05:00:54.023Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Wow, great bottle here. Dense and aromatic. Full of flowers, pears, lemons. Slight reduction, mineraled finish. My first Lorenzon white, but not my last.  I won\u2019t mention P/Q so as not to trigger anyone <img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/images/emoji/unicode/wink.png?v=12\" title=\":wink:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":wink:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/original/3X/5/a/5a79b70e0494843110ad230bf5b916d92550cf73.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/5a79b70e0494843110ad230bf5b916d92550cf73\" title=\"Lorenzon blanc\"><img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/5/a/5a79b70e0494843110ad230bf5b916d92550cf73_2_375x500.jpeg\" alt=\"Lorenzon blanc\" data-base62-sha1=\"cUnKegYr0Uj3xsbPgVkh94YaLBh\" width=\"375\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/5/a/5a79b70e0494843110ad230bf5b916d92550cf73_2_375x500.jpeg, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/5/a/5a79b70e0494843110ad230bf5b916d92550cf73_2_562x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/5/a/5a79b70e0494843110ad230bf5b916d92550cf73_2_750x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"38342D\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Lorenzon blanc</span><span class=\"informations\">1920\u00d72560 358 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>",
